Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.81,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}活生生出现在我的银幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:53.62,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我爱人的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:58.28,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我战斗时的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:07.61,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}全部都在我的脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:12.79,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我们一天的时间 让我们找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:17.07,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}引领到你世界的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:22.01,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我一个晚上 让你能再看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:25.51,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我就会相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:29.54,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:35.53,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,2000)}{\be1}回忆啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,=========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:22.53,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}没有地图 也没有罗盘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:27.57,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我们 扬帆出航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:37.11,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}并非去寻找既有的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:47.62,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}而是创造全新世界之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:57.80,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}过去的旅途仍记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:03.87,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}不论是哪一段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:11.21,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}都是一段很热闹的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:33.46,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回头望去 旅程激起的波浪浮现
